### Proposed Resolution: Execute P0 items first (idea_to_spec upgrade, assumption_testing, go_no_go_gate) as they provide the highest leverage with the least dependency complexity. The idea_to_spec upgrade (Order 1) is a pure edit to an existing file with zero dependencies — it can be done immediately.
### Cross-Phase Impact: Full P0+P1 implementation transforms Phase 1 from a collection of loosely connected skills into a validated, gated, evidence-driven phase that produces a PRD as its primary output. Phase 2 becomes architecturally grounded, Phase 4 receives security requirements already specified, and Phase 5 launches with a validated business model.
